data.description: Beautifully maintained home with a few extras.... Welcoming porch allows entryway into the 10' ceilings in common area up to 11' in living area, 9' ceilings throughout remainder of home. The hardwood floors in entry, dining, and living areas, along with tile in wet areas allow for a nice flow, along with the custom wood cabinets and granite. Enjoy the whirlpool tub in owner's suite, along with a seperate shower, double vanities, extra parking, fully covered back porch area, walk-in storage underneath house, along with other little extras throughout this wonderful home.
